followsFromBackgroundKnowledge

protected boolean followsFromBackgroundKnowledge(de.tudresden.inf.tcs.fcaapi.FCAImplication<A> implication)
Description copied from class: AbstractContext
Checks whether an implication already follows from some background knowledge, in case it exists. For instance, in a DL context it would check if a given implication (in this case a subsumption relation) already follows from the DL knowledge base.

Specified by:
